com.paco.java.subway

Class NodeLinker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paco.java.subway.NodeLinker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INodeLinker
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NodeLinkTable

    public class NodeLinker
extends java.lang.Object
implements INodeLinker
    This class is a shadow class of the NodeLink class. It is used to strictly carry the distance between 2 Nodes and doesn't handle the linking of the 2 Nodes. Therefore instance of this class can be used to compute the distance of any 2 Nodes... This class implements the INodeLinker Interface
    Author:
    Pascal
